title: Is NAFTA doomed? Canada may pivot to China for free trade
description:
Christopher Wilson of The Rebel.Media reports: After the fifth round of NAFTA re-negotiations, all sides left Mexico City as far away from striking a new deal as they've ever been, but is Canada being authentic in efforts to secure a new deal with the U.S. or does Trudeau's contempt for Trump mean we’ll be shifting our focus to free trade with China? 
MORE:  https://www.therebel.media/is_nafta_doomed_canada_appears_ready_to_pivot_to_china_for_free_trade
